    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "This is a 75 year old with a  history  of Severe HTN, CAD, spinal    stenosis, H",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s1",
      "text": "This is a 75 year old with a  history  of Severe HTN, CAD, spinal    stenosis, Hypothyroid, OA, Scoliosis, Diverticulitis, Hiatal Hernia, L    shoulder injury, L knee torn cartilage, r Knee tumor, psoriasis, TIA,    CRI, CABG x4 and MVR, B/L cataract, R Knee tumor resection, PTCA and    Stent x2."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "She was admitted on the [**1-6**] for pre angio hydration  On [**1-7**]    She u",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s2",
      "text": "She was admitted on the [**1-6**] for pre angio hydration  On [**1-7**]    She underwent an angiogram of bilateral lower extremities, Abdominal    Aortogram and Stenting of right common iliac artery stenosis and right    external iliac artery stenosis."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Around 1730 yesterday she developed a    severe headache along with word finding",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s3",
      "text": "Around 1730 yesterday she developed a    severe headache along with word finding and memory difficulties    daughter felt she had some left sided weakness and facial weakness."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Of    note her blood pressure was 220 s Then episode lasted up to 45 minutes    ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s4",
      "text": "Of    note her blood pressure was 220 s Then episode lasted up to 45 minutes    pt was sent for a head CT which was negative but blood pressure    remained out of control so she was transferred to CVICU for a labetolol    drip."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Peripheral vascular disease (PVD) with critical limb ischemia    Assessment:    ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s5",
      "text": "Peripheral vascular disease (PVD) with critical limb ischemia    Assessment:    Alert and oriented X3."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Speech clear and normal.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s6",
      "text": "Speech clear and normal."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Moves all extremities    with good strength.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s7",
      "text": "Moves all extremities    with good strength."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "L upper arm slightly weak r/t prior L shoulder    injury.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s8",
      "text": "L upper arm slightly weak r/t prior L shoulder    injury."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Follows commands.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s9",
      "text": "Follows commands."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:10",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Continues to c/o frontal headache-treated with    Tylenol, cold compresses and i",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row399595#s10",
      "text": "Continues to c/o frontal headache-treated with    Tylenol, cold compresses and ice packs with slight relief.    50-60 SB without VEA."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row399595:11",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "SBP 150-160 s/ On heparin gtt at 500 units/hr    for PTT >150.",
      "code": null,
